cu.explanation_en: Setting the ciphering algorithm to the unknown enum 'nea9' will cause negotiation failure during the security negotiation phase and NAS registration rejection.

du.explanation_en: Setting phy_log_level to an invalid enum value 'invalid' will cause log configuration parsing failure.
du.explanation_zh: 將 phy_log_level 設定為無效的枚舉值 'invalid' 會導致日誌配置解析失敗。
